structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS
COUNTY GOVERNMENT (FISCAL COURTS AND COUNTY COMMISSIONERS)

law.history: Repealed 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 118, sec. 19, effective June 17, 1978. -- Created 1956 Ky. Acts ch. 85, sec. 1.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Fiscal courts authorized to appropriate and donate funds to nonprofit corporations or associations organized for recreation or conservation purposes -- Conditions.
